casebody.data:
No. 11-189. Colony Cove Properties, LLC, Petitioner v. City of Carson, California, et al. 565 U.S. 971, 132 S. Ct. 456,

181 L. Ed. 2d 308,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7510. October 17, 2011.

Motion of Cato Institute, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of Western Manufactured Housing Communities Association for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 640 F.3d 948.
